description: Gorgeous water views!!!!     The living area and master bedroom in this perfectly sized two bedroom home look directly onto Boston Harbor--- watch the sail boats see the ferries, enjoy the breathtaking views!!!!  This is a like -new home with custom built in automatic window treatments, subzero/wolf appliances including a wine chiller,  Italian custom cabinetry, and wide plank hardwood flooring throughout the living and bedroom areas.  There is also an Air Lux window system that allows a full window to open onto the Harbor with a simple press of a button creating a balcony effect from the living area.   The St Regis is a five star full service building which is located in the center of Boston's famous seaport.  Residents enjoy a swimming pool, fitness center, business center, beautifully appointed social room and 2 guest suites.  There is a 24 hour concierge .  Enjoy priority seating at the popular Savr Restaurant which resides on the property. Parking is included with this home.
